<item>
            <title>[DERBY-3763] Rename BaseJDBCTestCase.usingDerbyNet</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-3763</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The names of the methods &apos;usingDerbyNet&apos; and &apos;usingDerbyNetClient&apos; in BaseJDBCTestCase are confusing.&lt;br/&gt;
I propose we change the one used to tell if we are using the DB2 client driver (JCC).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
